if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"咁你應該屌毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2111bbeea3f51aed00df5d35b19aa92af0b04a","tid":1819164,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"結後語：等待黎明來到"}]}